Package at.tugraz.kmi.medokyservice.fca.rest.wrappers

This Package contains a set of wrappers and helper classes for use with the REST Interface

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractWrapper
    Base class for all wrappers used by the FCA REST inteface
    ConceptWrapper
    Wrapper class resembling a Concept or a LearnerConcept but without cyclic or nested references used by LatticeWrapper.
    CourseWrapper  
    DomainBlueprint
    Wrapper used for serving domain metadata (name, description id) and for creating domains based on a mapping of FCAObjects to FCAAttributes.
    DomainWrapper
    Wrapper user for (de-)serializing a domain from/to JSON
    LatticeWrapper
    Wrapper used by the REST Interface to transmit a Lattice without any nested or cyclic references.
    LearningObjectWrapper
    Wrapper class to create LearningObjects
    UpdateWrapper
    Wrapper used to receive valuations
    UserWrapper
    Wrapper class for creating a User throigh the REST interface
    ValuationWrapper
